      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marco Costalba</b>\n</p><p><b>Marco Costalba</b>,<br />\nan Italian software developer and proponent of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_source\">open source</a> software <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. Marco is author of <i>QGit</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , a GUI of the free distributed version control system <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Git_%28software%29\">Git</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, initially designed and developed by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linus_Torvalds\">Linus Torvalds</a> for <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux_kernel\">kernel</a> development.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Stockfish\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Stockfish</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2008_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2008 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Costalba&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Stockfish\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Based on <a href=\"/Tord_Romstad\" title=\"Tord Romstad\">Tord Romstad's</a> <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess program</a> <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a> under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public License</a>, he started a branch called <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> in 2008 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, which in the meantime has become the main branch of Glaurung, further supported by Tord Romstad and <a href=\"/Joona_Kiiski\" title=\"Joona Kiiski\">Joona Kiiski</a> as development team <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Costalba&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2008_...\">2008 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Costalba&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2008 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22732\">Monte carlo on a NVIDIA GPU&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 01, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/GPU\" title=\"GPU\">GPU</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23860\">Superlinear interpolator: a nice novelity&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 20, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24675\">Stockfish 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 02, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24771\">Please drop Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=234691&amp;t=25118&amp;sid=5d8f3f4a0d7f4c59a93e786c21c00072\">Re: relative history heuristic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 30, 2008 &#160;» <a href=\"/Relative_History_Heuristic\" title=\"Relative History Heuristic\">Relative History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=25317\">Null driven IID</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2009</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=267994&amp;t=27965\">Piece attacks count</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 18, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=285407\">Cache pollution when reading/writing hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 09, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30624\">Likelihood of superiority</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#Likelihood_of_superiority\" title=\"Match Statistics\">LOS</a>, <a href=\"/LOS_Table\" title=\"LOS Table\">LOS Table</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Costalba&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32148\">Avoiding qsearch explosion</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34633\">DTS-ification of YBWC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Young_Brothers_Wait_Concept\" title=\"Young Brothers Wait Concept\">Young Brothers Wait Concept</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=367314&amp;t=35841\">Re: Extended Null-Move Reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2011</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39298\">Build magics on the fly</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 07, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a>, <a href=\"/Looking_for_Magics\" title=\"Looking for Magics\">Looking for Magics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39593\">Is Rybka that needs ICGA or the opposite&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 03, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a>, <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=439431&amp;t=41597\">Re: Razoring</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 26, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class