"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45406\">LOS calculation: Does the same result is always the same?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics#Likelihood_of_superiority\" title=\"Match Statistics\">LOS</a>, <a href=\"/LOS_Table\" title=\"LOS Table\">LOS Table</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2013</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47885\">Fishtest Distributed Testing Framework</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 01, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish#Fishtest\" title=\"Stockfish\">Fishtest</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49035\">Stockfish 4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49062\">Tuning for rating lists&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Contempt_Factor\" title=\"Contempt Factor\">Contempt Factor</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50275\">Stockfish DD: a new official release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_5\" title=\"TCEC Season 5\">TCEC Season 5</a>, dedicated to <a href=\"/Don_Dailey\" title=\"Don Dailey\">Don Dailey</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2014</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52487\">Stockfish 5</a> by <a class=\"mw