C\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2016&#160;»  <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a>, <a href=\"/Python\" title=\"Python\">Python</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/LCoojE9O5jU/h6xgvg2EBgAJ\">Stockfish 8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, November 01, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61924\">Stockfish 8 official</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 01, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62452\">Scoutfish: powerful chess query tool</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Databases</a>, <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Scoutfish&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Scoutfish (page does not exist)\">Scoutfish</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2017</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54697&amp;start=50\">Re: Chessprogams with the most chessknowing</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Knowledge#SearchVersusEvaluation\" title=\"Knowledge\">Search versus Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60312&amp;start=240\">Natural TB (take 2)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"C